notes: England's 1st match against Pakistan in Pakistan since 1987/88.
DG Cork acted as a runner for RA Smith for part of his innings.
RA Smith and MA Atherton 147 for the 1st wicket, highest partnership for any wicket by England against Pakistan, first ever century partnership for the 1st wicket at Karachi.
PAJ DeFreitas and AJ Stewart substituted for Fairbrother and Smith in the field.
